cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with music genre classification using neural networks, which falls under the broad category of multimedia (cs.MM). The use of conditional and masked conditional neural networks also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation of the performance of the networks on datasets suggests a focus on information retrieval (cs.IR) and statistical learning (cs.SD).
